des: The Chattanooga History skill features an assortment of facts regarding the history of Chattanooga. Includes history about the start and foundation of Chattanooga, the Civil War, industrialization, links to the current landscape, and more! Simply start the skill and you will be given one random historic fact about Chattanooga each time.
